    "We carefully reviewed each LLM's licensing agreement, including factors such usage restrictions, business feasibility, and intellectual property rights.Lastly, we assessed each LLM provider's overall offering and associated costs.",
    "While performance and functionality were our main concerns, we also took long-term cost implications, support services, and pricing structures into account to ensure the sustainability and scalability of our AI Study Partner system.By carefully assessing these characteristics, we aimed to select an LLM that not only suited our immediate research goals but also provided a solid foundation for future enhancements and real-world use of our AI Study Partner system.",
    "RESULT & DISCUSSIONStudents' learning experiences have been significantly improved by the AI Study Partner system.",
    "The system has successfully met the various needs of learners with its array of features, which includes conversational chatbot assistance, flashcard creation, summarization, automated question development, and intelligent search capabilities.The beneficial effect on retention and engagement is one of the main conclusions.",
    "Because the AI Study Partner offered a tailored and adaptable approach to learning, students reported feeling more motivated and interested in the material."
